{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会使用停表</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量时间。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">停表</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">是测量</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时间</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的常用工具</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">停表</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.练习使用停表。按动停表上的按钮，观察指针（或数字）的变化，了解停表的使用方法。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.用停表测量</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">脉搏跳动</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次的时间。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.用停表测量</span>1 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">min<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">脉搏跳动的次数</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">读数时小盘的分钟数</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大盘的秒读数。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">脉搏跳动</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">10<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">次的时间为</span>8s<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.1 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">min<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">脉搏跳动的次数</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为</span>70-80<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">左右。</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多次测量取平均值可减小实验误差。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测量时计时点要与计数点保持一致；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">读数时要注意小盘中指针是否超过半分钟刻度。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}